headline: Chase and The Points Guy Launch Sweepstakes in Support of Make-A-Wish
summary: Chase and The Points Guy (TPG) are teaming up for the launch of a new sweepstakes benefiting Make-A-Wish®, inviting supporters to help grant life-changing wishes for children with critical illnesses and enter for a chance to win 1 million Chase Ultimate Rewards® points and a private planning session for a bucket-list worthy trip with Brian Kelly, founder of The Points Guy.
